caseFile.title: Learning Objectives
caseFile.content: Students will understand contract law principles and identify inconsistencies in business agreements.

caseFile.title: Smith vs. Jones Contract Dispute
caseFile.content: ABC Company signed a contract with XYZ Corp on March 15, 2024 for $50,000 worth of services to be delivered within 30 days.

caseFile.title: John Smith - CEO Testimony
caseFile.content: I clearly remember signing the contract with XYZ Corp on March 16, 2024. The amount was $45,000 and we agreed to a 45-day delivery timeline.

caseFile.title: Signed Contract
caseFile.content: Contract between ABC Company and XYZ Corporation. Date: March 15, 2024. Amount: $50,000. Delivery period: 30 days from signing.
